Additional warranty period: Technical component, Description: The contracting authority awards points for offers that present an additional warranty period beyond the minimum warranty of 24 months requested.
Calculation method: Additional points are assigned for each year of warranty and for additional services offered beyond the minimum technical specifications as follows:
+ 0 years of additional warranty: 0 points;
+ 1 year of additional warranty: 5 points;
+ 2 years of additional warranty: 10 points;
+ 3 years of additional warranty: 15 points;
+ 4 or more years of additional warranty: 20 points.

The bidder shall present, in the technical proposal, a written statement detailing the offered period and certifying that the goods comply with the contract specifications, including all indicated uses.
